 Kontext und auf der Suche nach mehr Leichtigkeit im Sprechen über den Islam.  aHow are contemporary sociopolitical questions dealt with in the theater? This study throws light on theatrical productions that deal with the themes of migration and Islam.  afunded by Berlin Graduate School Muslim Cultures and Societies (BGSMCS)  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Jun 2022) 4aEinwanderungsgesellschaft. 4aIdentitätspolitik. 4aIslam. 4aIslamfeindlichkeit. 4aIslamwissenschaft. 4aKulturproduktion. 4aKörper. 4aMigration. 4aPolitisches Theater. 4aPostkolonialismus. 4aRepräsentation. 4aStuart Hall. 4aTheater. 4aTheaterwissenschaft. 7aPERFORMING ARTS / Theater / History & Criticism.2bisacsh  aBody.  aCultural Production.  aIdentity Politics.  aImmigration Society.  aIslam.  aIslamic Studies.  aIslamophobia.  aMigration.  aPolitical Theatre.  aPostcolonialism.  aRepresentation.  aStuart Hall.  aTheatre Studies.  aTheatre.2 aBerlin Graduate School Muslim Cultures and Societies (BGSMCS)efunder.4fnd4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/fnd08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2021 Part 2z978311074335708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2022 Part 2z978311076700108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Arts 2021z9783110753790oZDB-23-DPK08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021z9783110753776oZDB-23-DGG0 cprintz978383763007740uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839430071?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839430071423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839430071/original  a978-3-11-074335-7  DG Plus PP Package 2021 Part 2b2021  a978-3-11-076700-1  DG Plus PP Package 2022 Part 2b2022  aEBA_CL_MUAR  aEBA_EBKALL 